<solution>
<p><ul><li>6.608319273679</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={300}{e}^{{{0.08}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{509}={300}{e}^{{{0.08}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{509}}{{300}}={e}^{{{0.08}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{509}}{{300}}\right)}}}={0.08}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{509}}{{300}}\right)}}}}{{0.08}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={6.608319273679}</m></p>
</solution>
